## Usage Patterns

### Basic

```tsx
() => (
  <Flair colorStyle={1} style={{ marginBottom: '4px' }}>
    Flair Label
  </Flair>
)
```

### Sizes

```tsx
() => (
  <div
    style={{
      display: 'flex',
      flexDirection: 'column',
      flexWrap: 'wrap',
      gap: '16px'
    }}
  >
    {sizes.map((size) => (
      <div key={size}>
        <h3>{upperCaseUtil(size)}</h3>
        <Flair colorStyle={1} size={size} style={{ marginRight: '8px' }}>
          Flair Label
        </Flair>
        <br />
      </div>
    ))
```

## Guidelines

**Use when:**
- To highlight or emphasize specific pieces of information.


## Code Example

```tsx
import Flair from `@ids-ts/flair`;

<Flair size="medium" colorStyle={1}>
  New
</Flair>;
```

